{
 "cells": [
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# 复合材料层板层间应力计算\n",
    "\n",
    "本notebook演示了如何使用经典层板理论(CLT)和一阶剪切变形理论(FSDT)计算复合材料层板在弯曲载荷下的层间应力。"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
    "from composite_laminates import CompositeLaminate, plot_stress_distribution\n",
    "\n",
    "%matplotlib inline"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 1. 定义材料属性和铺层"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# T300/环氧复合材料属性\n",
    "ply_properties = {\n",
    "    'E1': 138e9,      # 纵向弹性模量 (Pa)\n",
    "    'E2': 8.96e9,     # 横向弹性模量 (Pa)\n",
    "    'G12': 7.1e9,     # 面内剪切模量 (Pa)\n",
    "    'G13': 7.1e9,     # 横向剪切模量 (Pa)\n",
    "    'G23': 3.9e9,     # 横向剪切模量 (Pa)\n",
    "    'nu12': 0.3       # 泊松比\n",
    "}\n",
    "\n",
    "# 对称铺层 [0/45/-45/90]s\n",
    "layup = [0, 45, -45, 90, 90, -45, 45, 0]\n",
    "ply_thickness = 0.125e-3  # 单层厚度 (m)\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f\"铺层角度: {layup}\")\n",
    "print(f\"总层数: {len(layup)}\")\n",
    "print(f\"总厚度: {len(layup) * ply_thickness * 1000:.2f} mm\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 2. 创建层板对象并应用弯曲载荷"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 创建层板对象\n",
    "laminate = CompositeLaminate(ply_properties, layup, ply_thickness)\n",
    "\n",
    "# 应用弯曲载荷\n",
    "Mx = 100.0  # x方向弯矩 (N·m/m)\n",
    "My = 50.0   # y方向弯矩 (N·m/m)\n",
    "Mxy = 0.0   # 扭矩 (N·m/m)\n",
    "\n",
    "laminate.apply_bending_load(Mx=Mx, My=My, Mxy=Mxy)\n",
    "\n",
    "# 打印摘要\n",
    "laminate.print_summary()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 3. 计算层间剪应力 (CLT方法)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "z_clt, tau_xz_clt, tau_yz_clt = laminate.calculate_interlaminar_shear_stress()\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f\"最大层间剪应力 τ_xz (CLT): {np.max(np.abs(tau_xz_clt)):.3e} Pa\")\n",
    "print(f\"最大层间剪应力 τ_yz (CLT): {np.max(np.abs(tau_yz_clt)):.3e} Pa\")\n",
    "print(f\"中面处 τ_xz: {tau_xz_clt[len(tau_xz_clt)//2]:.3e} Pa\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 4. 计算层间剪应力 (FSDT方法)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 假设剪力\n",
    "Qx = 1000  # x方向剪力 (N/m)\n",
    "Qy = 500   # y方向剪力 (N/m)\n",
    "\n",
    "z_fsdm, tau_xz_fsdm, tau_yz_fsdm = laminate.calculate_fsdm_shear_stress(Qx, Qy)\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f\"最大层间剪应力 τ_xz (FSDT): {np.max(np.abs(tau_xz_fsdm)):.3e} Pa\")\n",
    "print(f\"最大层间剪应力 τ_yz (FSDT): {np.max(np.abs(tau_yz_fsdm)):.3e} Pa\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 5. 计算层间剥离应力"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "z_peel, sigma_z = laminate.calculate_peeling_stress()\n",
    "\n",
    "print(f\"最大剥离应力 σ_z: {np.max(np.abs(sigma_z)):.3e} Pa\")\n",
    "print(f\"中面处剥离应力: {sigma_z[len(sigma_z)//2]:.3e} Pa\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 6. 绘制应力分布图"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "fig = plot_stress_distribution(laminate, title_prefix=\"[0/45/-45/90]s \")\n",
    "fig.savefig('composite_stresses.png', dpi=300, bbox_inches='tight')\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 7. 各层面内应力详情"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "print(\"各层面内应力:\")\n",
    "print(\"=\"*80)\n",
    "for k, layer in enumerate(laminate.layer_stresses):\n",
    "    print(f\"\\n第{k+1}层 (θ={layer['theta']}°):\")\n",
    "    print(f\"  底面 (z={layer['z_bottom']*1000:.3f}mm): \")\n",
    "    print(f\"    σx={layer['sigma_bottom'][0]:.3e} Pa, σy={layer['sigma_bottom'][1]:.3e} Pa, τxy={layer['sigma_bottom'][2]:.3e} Pa\")\n",
    "    print(f\"  顶面 (z={layer['z_top']*1000:.3f}mm): \")\n",
    "    print(f\"    σx={layer['sigma_top'][0]:.3e} Pa, σy={layer['sigma_top'][1]:.3e} Pa, τxy={layer['sigma_top'][2]:.3e} Pa\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 8. 自定义铺层分析示例"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# 示例：分析不同铺层的影响\n",
    "layups = {\n",
    '[0]8': [0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0],\n",
    '[0/90]4s': [0, 90, 0, 90, 90, 0, 90, 0],\n",
    '[±45]4s': [45, -45, 45, -45, -45, 45, -45, 45]\n",
    "}\n",
    "\n",
    "print(\"不同铺层的弯曲刚度比较:\")\n",
    "print(\"=\"*60)\n",
    "for name, layup in layups.items():\n",
    "    lam = CompositeLaminate(ply_properties, layup, ply_thickness)\n",
    "    print(f\"\\n{name}:\")\n",
    "    print(f\"  D11 = {lam.D[0,0]:.3e} N·m\")\n",
    "    print(f\"  D22 = {lam.D[1,1]:.3e} N·m\")\n",
    "    print(f\"  D66 = {lam.D[2,2]:.3e} N·m\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 总结\n",
    "\n",
    "本程序实现了：\n",
    "1. **经典层板理论 (CLT)** - 计算ABD矩阵、面内应力和层间剪应力\n",
    "2. **一阶剪切变形理论 (FSDT)** - 考虑剪切变形的层间剪应力计算\n",
    "3. **层间剥离应力** - 近似计算方法\n",
    "\n",
    "### 关键公式：\n",
    "- ABD矩阵: A=∫Q̄dz, B=∫Q̄zdz, D=∫Q̄z²dz\n",
    "- 层间剪应力: τxz = -∫(dσx/dx + dτxy/dy)dz\n",
    "- FSDT剪应力: τxz = k * Qx / (A55) * G13 * (1 - z²/h²)"
   ]
  }
 ],
